<div id="tabs-5"  class="ui-tabs-panel">
<h2  align="center">Instructions</h2>
<p>
This product shows the predicted probability for epidemic experience due to the environmental factors of absolute humidity and land-cover type. </p><p>
This model does not include the impact of nonenvironmental factors likely to be related to meningitis epidemics, such as population movement, vaccination coverage and recent epidemics in the area.</p>

<p> Users should note that these data are based on a statistical model that exhibited a sensitivity and specificity of 83% and 67%, respectively. </p>


